question: Which group of organisms would all be found living in a tropical rain forest?
candidate_answers: (A) Lizards, insects, cacti, kangaroos (B) Vines, palm trees, tree frogs, monkeys (C) Evergreens, moose, weasels, mink (D) Lichens, mosses, caribou, polar bears
answer: Vines, palm trees, tree frogs, monkeys
label: B
